### Khela round-lifecycle smoke test.
### Run the API with the HTTP profile so HTTPS-redirect doesn't interfere:
###   dotnet run --launch-profile http
### Needs MySQL + Redis up. Execute the requests top to bottom.

@host = http://localhost:5044
@email = smoke1@khela.game
@password = Passw0rd
@bet = 1000

### 1) Register (first run). On re-runs this 400s "email exists" — use step 1b instead.
# @name register
POST {{host}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{ "email": "{{email}}", "username": "smoke1", "password": "{{password}}", "countryCode": "bd", "deviceId": "" }

### 1b) Login (use on subsequent runs instead of register)
# @name login
POST {{host}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{ "email": "{{email}}", "password": "{{password}}", "deviceId": "" }

### Token from whichever of 1/1b you ran (edit .register -> .login if you logged in)
@token = {{register.response.body.$.token}}

### 2) Wallet HUD — provisions starter chips (10000) + gems (100) on first call
GET {{host}}/api/wallet/balances
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3) Lobby — browsable tables (auto-seeds 3 Classic house tables on first hit)
# @name lobby
GET {{host}}/api/lobby/blackjack
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Grab the first table's id (the 1K/10K Classic table)
@tableId = {{lobby.response.body.$[0].tableId}}

### 4) Join — seats you from the WALLET balance (request balance is ignored). Takes seat 1.
POST {{host}}/api/blackjack/{{tableId}}/join
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "name": "SmokeTester", "image": "", "balance": 0 }

### 5) Place a bet on seat 1 (must be within table min/max)
POST {{host}}/api/blackjack/{{tableId}}/bet
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "amount": {{bet}}, "seatNumber": 1, "handIndex": 0 }

### 6) Deal — debits nothing yet (net-reconciled at settle); deals a seeded 6-deck shoe
POST {{host}}/api/blackjack/{{tableId}}/deal
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 7) Stand on seat 1 (or use /hit/1?handIndex=0 to draw)
POST {{host}}/api/blackjack/{{tableId}}/stand/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 8) Dealer plays + settles → wallet credited/debited by the net result + hand persisted
POST {{host}}/api/blackjack/{{tableId}}/dealerPlay
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 9) Balance again — should reflect the round's win/loss
GET {{host}}/api/wallet/balances
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 10) Board — dealer hole card now revealed; note "fairness" (commitment) block
GET {{host}}/api/blackjack/{{tableId}}/board
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 11) VERIFY a settled hand (public, no auth). Get the HandId from the GameHandHeaders
###     table in MySQL (newest row), then:
# GET {{host}}/api/blackjack/verify/PASTE-HANDID-HERE
